{"id":"fh_1700209164668","created_at":1700209164668,"updated_at":1706860448619,"title":"项目管理","data":{"root":{"data":{"text":"项目管理","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmh5c3kiw0","created":1706778480036,"text":"流程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmhc8fmiw0","created":1706778495052,"text":"1. 建立需求池","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmhuhh9280","created":1706778534781,"text":"便于了解短期、长期的产品项目规划","expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmi02vesw0","created":1706778546959,"text":"设置优先级，优先保障高优的需求支持落地"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cytmhg1e69s0","created":1706778503334,"text":"2. 提前沟通"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmibtw4jk0","created":1706778572537,"text":"提前于产品沟通需求任务，该拆解的拆解，高优的往前提，不合适的打回，分阶段支持"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmj8nn66w0","created":1706778643993,"text":"内部沟通，避免再评审出现较大争议时出现争执"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cytmhijzw6o0","created":1706778508812,"text":" 3.评审"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmjn9scns0","created":1706778675807,"text":"需求方案评审"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmjp45uww0","created":1706778679821,"text":"复杂业务的反串讲"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmjvnur400","created":1706778694072,"text":"技术方案评审"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmjxse5h40","created":1706778698700,"text":"重点：小事大会，大事小会，重要的事不开会"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cytmhm07bjs0","created":1706778516322,"text":"4. 排期"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmk8ghck00","created":1706778721924,"text":"排期包含：开发+自测+联调+上线+回归验证，需要预留足够的缓冲时间"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmklgyiwg0","created":1706778750251,"text":"高优先级的先做，往前排，优先支持保障；应对出现变故时，减小风险系数"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"cytmhnykuao0","created":1706778520578,"text":"5. 开发上线"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmlaxnjz40","created":1706778805680,"text":"6.效果追踪"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"cytmlipbkqw0","created":1706778822591,"text":"需求or项目上线之后，再跟一下，看下表现情况，相关数据指标如何"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"cytmlqhdepc0","created":1706778839524,"text":"通过效果的追踪反馈，一方面更了解业务，另一方面也可以认识到自己工作的价值"},"ch